</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B9898347E53FFDFFF3F746ADDDDF8A3" blockId="33.[192,707,1856,1881]" box="[192,707,1856,1881]" pageId="33" pageNumber="32">
<emphasis id="B95344267E53FFDFFF3F746ADEAEF8A3" bold="true" box="[192,432,1856,1880]" pageId="33" pageNumber="32">Species included.</emphasis>
Only the 
<typeStatus id="549C26967E53FFDFFDD6746BDD40F8A2" box="[553,606,1857,1881]" pageId="33" pageNumber="32">type</typeStatus>
species.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B9898347E53FFDFFF3F745ADC29F872" blockId="33.[192,823,1904,1929]" box="[192,823,1904,1929]" pageId="33" pageNumber="32">
<emphasis id="B95344267E53FFDFFF3F745ADE62F873" bold="true" box="[192,380,1904,1928]" pageId="33" pageNumber="32">Parent taxon.</emphasis>
Subtribe Moncina A. 
<bibRefCitation id="EFB6E5C57E53FFDFFD78745BDC2DF872" author="Warren, A. D. &amp; J. R. Ogawa &amp; A. V. Z. Brower" box="[647,819,1905,1929]" journalOrPublisher="Phylogenetic relationships of subfamilies and circumscription of tribes in the family Hesperiidae (Lepidoptera: Hesperioidea). Cladistics" pageId="33" pageNumber="32" pagination="642 - 676" part="24" refId="ref28580" refString="Warren, A. D., J. R. Ogawa, and A. V. Z. Brower. 2008. Phylogenetic relationships of subfamilies and circumscription of tribes in the family Hesperiidae (Lepidoptera: Hesperioidea). Cladistics 24 (5): 642 - 676." type="journal article" year="2008">Warren, 2008</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
